Leaders affiliated to Wiper Party have expressed their views on the 2022 succession politics, saying that for one to succeed, they must include the over 1.4 million votes from the Kamba community. MPs’ Patrick Makau, Stephen Mule and Ex-Machakos Senator Johnston Muthama have placed their bet on Kalonzo Musyoka to run for president in 2022 At the center of President Kenyatta’s succession talk is DP William Ruto among others, last week while on a tour of Mt Kenya region,  the president revealed that his 2022 pick will be a shocker. 